ComicInfo.Title: The Self-Preservation Society, Part Two
ComicInfo.Summary: With the Female gone and the survivors left reeling, the Boys find out who's after them the hard way - walking straight into a nightmarish trap. Pulping teenage supes is one thing, but how will our heroes fair against a front-rank supe team of unimaginable power? Blood flies and bones shatter, as Butcher decides to meet fire with fire... in The Self-Preservation Society, part two.
